rful one! If it is a comfortable day, enjoy it and invest in it for a lasting tomorrow’s comfort for you least know what in reality is ahead of you! Build a solid tomorrow today! Today is today; use it well!', 4606, 0), (144379, 'Purpose and reason? Purpose and reason are not the same thing. Reason seeks to understand. Purpose requires faith. Reason is attained. Purpose is revealed. Reason is acquired by works. Purpose is endowed with grace. And wisdom is the combination of both.', 10817, 0), (144380, 'The fire spread from the small cinder then the flames will become strong', 5136, 0), (144381, 'Ignorance shuts the mind’s door tight', 27204, 0), (144382, 'One who never reads only goes where his feet can take him, but one who does, travels around the world.', 5104, 0), (144383, 'You cannot tell a river in which direction it should flow, but you can steer your boat.', 5104, 0), (144384, 'A bee, though small, can still sting you; an elephant, though calm, can still trample you; a lion, though full, can still devour you.', 5104, 0), (144385, 'Pleasure is a kind servant, but a cruel master.', 5104, 0), (144386, 'Light is a beautiful servant', 27205, 0), (144387, 'Intelligence opens the door to the universe', 27206, 0), (144388, 'Sages see further with their eyes closed than scholars with their eyes open.', 5104, 0), (144389, 'It is never a river’s fault that one cannot swim.', 5104, 0), (144390, 'Know truth. Respect facts. Doubt opinions. Reject lies.', 5104, 0), (144391, 'Take your time to find and understand what you don’t know and in the end, you shall know that it is not all the things you know that shows you something you don’t know, but something you don’t know!', 4606, 0), (144392, 'Take your time to find, know and understand what you don’t know and in the end, you shall know that it is not all the things you know that show you something you don’t know, but something you don’t know!', 4606, 0), (144393, 'If the sun shone for itself, it would be blinded by its own 