others even those things that were not given unto it.', 103, 0), (144760, 'An open heart has greater power than a clenched fist.', 5104, 0), (144761, 'Do not live because of the fear of death. Live because of the fear of the death of the real reason why you live. Death is no respecter of persons. Death can come when we have not even given him our attention. Death doesn''t mind that you are in tension and even when you in the mid of doing something at his arrival, you shall go with nothing. The most important thing to death is to take you at a sudden. Mind your time then! Mind your true purpose! And mind the real reasons why you wake up each day and retire when the sun sets! Life is once, live it well!', 4606, 0), (144762, 'Think of something, Oh yes! Think of something. Your life must not be in retardation so think of something! Think of growth for that is the whole essence of life!', 4606, 0), (144763, 'I have two great duties in each day: firstly, to identify why I woke up and secondly to be convinced of why I must retire!', 4606, 0), (144764, 'true giving lies not in receiving but in giving', 4606, 0), (144765, 'Learn how to learn...then start learning', 2760, 0), (144766, 'One of the reasons for not being contented is our inability to accept things as they are, together with ourselves, other people, events and every little detail of our days.And we try to change the unchangeable and control the uncontrollable.', 15087, 0), (144767, 'They that pursue their dreams unrelentingly with tenacity and the right attitude never continue to live with dreams forever. They live their dreams and realize their aspirations.', 4606, 0), (144768, 'I have two great duties in each day: firstly, to identify why I woke up and secondly to be convinced of why I must retire for the day', 4606, 0), (144769, 'Wisdom comes easy to me today. The Universal Intelligence and the Cosmic Power, Empower me with wisdom each day of my life. Thanks BE to God. _nickc', 5145, 0), (144770, 'Every author loves to read his own words.', 27237, 0), (144771, 'Valid questions are better than invalid assumptions.', 5104, 0), (144772, 'Silence can answer the question words may fail to answer. If you want to know what silence can do, keep silence!', 4606, 0), (144773, 'to live and leave indelible footprints, think of the rocks', 4606, 0), (144774, 'Don''t judge a lion by its swimming abilities.', 5104, 0), (144775, 'There is always something worse, limit thinking about worse things and concentrate on the best things.', 4606, 0), (144776, 'It is in vain to wipe away tears in the rain.', 5104, 0), (144777, 'God created sages because He wanted to leave the light on in the universe.', 5104, 0), (144778, 'Butterflies can''t see their wings. They can''t see how truly beautiful they are, but everyone else can. People are like that as well.', 4603, 0), (144779, 'The blossoms fall just once each winter, yet in our memories, they fall every day.', 16499, 0), (144780, 'Give me a moment I am preparing to drawback to screamLouder than a train overhead below a railroad bridge', 21624, 0), (144781, 'if the storm of life gives you a big blow, don''t worry, just give it a great smile and pursue to leave distinctive footprints with perseverance and tenacity regardless of how arduous the errand may be. It may not be so easy but, dare to win!', 4606, 0), (144782, 'You can crush a rose', 27238, 0), (144783, 'though excessive pride may seek for freedom, it may only see freedom in chains', 4606, 0), (144784, 'You have no power over your past,but you do over your present.You have no power over your history,but you do over your future.You have no power over your fortune,but you do over your actions.You have no power over your reputation,but you do over your character.You have no power over destiny,but you do over yourself.You have no power over anyone,but you do over your world.', 5104, 0), (144785, 'The value of darkness can never be measuredif you don’t break its cheap spell secretly treasured'