INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (145001, 'Reaping from an opportunity is intelligence', 27271, 0), (145002, 'Love, no matter how small, begets kindness.Joy, no matter how small, begets cheerfulness.Wisdom, no matter how small, begets intelligence.Faith, no matter how small, begets persistence.Genius, no matter how small, begets excellence.', 5104, 0), (145003, 'Joy turns tears into laughter.Hope turns mourning into gladness.Wisdom turns tragedy into fortune.Faith turns defeat into triumph.Love turns enmity into friendship.', 5104, 0), (145004, 'Future never desires to become a past', 2760, 0), (145005, 'Letting go of sorrow gives you enough strength to carry happiness.Letting go of anger gives you enough strength to carry kindness.Letting go of fear gives you enough strength to carry hopefulness.Letting go of resentment gives you enough strength to carry gratefulness.Letting go of disappointment gives you enough strength to carry joyfulness.Letting go of avarice gives you enough strength to carry contentedness.', 5104, 0), (145006, 'Morality cannot replace goodness.Knowledge cannot replace wisdom.Fame cannot replace honor.Pleasure cannot replace contentment.Passion cannot replace love.', 5104, 0), (145007, 'The weaknesses of the wise are better than the strengths of fools.', 5104, 0), (145008, 'Whatever it is you want in this life, be it material things, a place you want to be, or an experience you want to have, you must first make it real in the realm of your consciousness.', 4863, 0), (145009, 'You cannot truly know pleasure without pain.You cannot truly know strength without weakness.You cannot truly know joy without sorrow.You cannot truly know hope without despair.', 5104, 0), (145010, 'Honey does not lose its sweetness because it is made by bees that sting.', 5104, 0), (145011, 'Love costs us much,but we still need it.Wisdom costs us much,but we still seek it.Faith costs us much,but we still practice it.Life costs us much,but we still desire it.', 5104, 0), (145012, 'Seek wisdom, and success will find you.', 5104, 0), (145013, 'Pain helps the body grow.Riddles help the mind grow.Loss helps the heart grow.Temptations help the soul grow.', 5104, 0), (145014, 'Avoid and ignore the idiots who try to bring you down in life', 27272, 0), (145015, 'Life is too short to hold grudges, plan vengeance, and be angry for too long. And people say things like that all the time, but words like that only take on their meaning when you experience someone close to you passing away. There are truly not enough minutes, hours, days, months, years, to spend any amount of time on being and doing anything other than going into the direction of your happiness. Acceptance is better than correction and joy is better than revenge. Innocent laughter is better than anger.', 103, 0), (145016, 'As soon as anger knocks at one’s door, wisdom prepares to leave.', 11038, 0), (145017, 'A lie has many colours, while white is the only faithful colour of truth.', 2760, 0), (145018, 'People spend their entire lives searching the world for the pieces that will make them whole, yet those pieces are only found within them.', 5043, 0), (145019, 'Your mockers will only have your attention only if you give them your attention', 4606, 0), (145020, 'We wait upon finite minds to validate infinite things— this is evidence of human stupidity.', 103, 0), (145021, 'one idiot can shut 1000 wise men mouths, where as 1000 wise will fail to open the eyes of an idiot.', 17579, 0), (145022, 'they that fail to recognize, take and and learn the lessons of discomfort well, meet the comforts of life and still live in discomfort', 4606, 0), (145023, 'The sun doesn’t live in England', 27273, 0), (145024, 'We can learn so much about the living, according to how they treat their dead. And we can see the true colours of people coming out, when we observe how they act and react, to the circumstances that come about after the death of a loved one. Lastly, we learn about the things most important in our lives, when we experience the loss called death. It is extraordinary how death can give back so much to life and to the living.', 103, 0), (145025, 'Courage is not the absence of fear. Hope is not the absence of trouble. Joy is not the absence of pain. Love is not the absence of obstacles.', 5104, 0), (145026, 'Bait, no matter how big, is useless if fish do not desire it.', 5104, 0), (145027, 'Half a brain is better than none.', 5104, 0), (145028, 'It is not for a vulture to teach an eagle how to hunt.', 5104, 0), (145029, 'Because a spoon is made of gold does not change the soup’s taste.', 5104, 0), (145030, 'Why weep when it takes less energy to laugh? Why frown when it takes less energy to smile? Why despair when it takes less energy to hope? Why fear when it takes less energy to love?', 5104, 0), (145031, 'Have gracious thoughts of your neighbors,kind thoughts of your friends,loving thoughts of your family,and humble thoughts of yourself.', 5104, 0), (145032, 'Coat your words with honey if you want to catch bees.', 5104, 0), (145033, 'The best way to catch a bee is using its own honey.', 5104, 0), (145034, 'No matter how much territory the wolf conquers the lion will still rule the jungle.', 5104, 0), (145035, 'Gray hairs signify old age, not wisdom.Muscles signify strength, not health.Laughter signifies amusement, not joy.Weeping signifies pain, not weakness.Smiling signifies courteousness, not love.', 5104, 0), (145036, 'What you were is yesterday.What you are is now.What you can be is tomorrow.What you decide to be is today.', 5104, 0), (145037, 'Slaves of wisdom are masters of many.', 5104, 0), (145038, 'People who are unable to stand within the dark places of life, those who are always running towards their happy places, are the same things as candles without flames. There is no worth in a candle without a flame, and we only add the flame when there is darkness. Without darkness, there would be no need for warriors and angels. Warriors are not made because the whole world is happy and angels were not formed because there are no demons. Be of worth, have a flame.', 103, 0), (145039, 'Out of frustrations, out of desperation, out of disappointments, out of mediocrity. out of idleness,out of limited insight, out of difficulties, out of insatiability, out of poverty, out of pain and the vicissitudes of life , so many people shall come to a conclusion that nothing is worth living for; not even what is solemn and sacred but, some shall always turn the woes of life into great land marks and indelible footprints worth emulating', 4606, 0), (145040, 'When family gathers around for a dying loved one, I have realised, that it probably does more good for the living, than for the dying. Sometimes, death can bring the living together, and death can cause the living to find solace in one another. In this way, death is a part of life, and those who die can in fact give gifts to the living, gifts that they were not able to give while they were still alive and well.', 103, 0), (145041, 'It is impossible for a man to outpace his shadow.', 5104, 0), (145042, 'Soft feathers cannot make a cruel bird kind', 2760, 0), (145043, 'Childishness and childlikeness are two very different things. To know a childlike person, is to know a very mature person; to know a childish person, is to know a very immature person. To know childlikeness is to know original wisdom; to know childishness is to know original error. And there are many children more mature than adults, many adults less mature than children.', 103, 0), (145044, 'The bigger the victory, the bigger the battle. Still, be the light and a change agent for healing, restoration and transformation.', 2736, 0), (145045, 'Wind has no feet,but travels great distances,and has no hands,but carries great objects.', 5104, 0), (145046, 'True freedom is in not having a master, but in making the master your slave', 3682, 0), (145047, 'If you think you can''t, you''re wrong and right', 3682, 0), (145048, 'Your chronological age makes you older, grownNess is a state of mind!', 27274, 0), (145049, 'Without our ancestors we would not be.', 27275, 0), (145050, 'A slap from an angel will make you wiserthan a kiss from the devil.', 5104, 0);
